      • getSeniority

        @RosettaSynonym(value="seniority",
                source="FpML")
 @RosettaAttribute(scheme="creditSeniorityScheme")
public final CreditSeniorityEnum getSeniority()
        The repayment precedence of a debt instrument, as specified by a set of enumerated values. FpML specifies that creditSeniorityTradingScheme (specified in the CDM through the CreditSeniorityTradingEnum) overrides creditSeniorityScheme (specified in the CDM through the CreditSeniorityEnum) when the underlyer defines the reference obligation used in a single name credit default swap trade.
